'''Dannemora''' is a new residential [[suburb]] in [[Auckland]], [[New Zealand]]. It is located in the east of the city, close to [[Pakuranga]] and [[Botany Downs, New Zealand|Botany Downs]], and in the new Howick ward, one of the thirteen administrative areas of Auckland city.
